text:
(upbeat music)
- My name is Nikita Jaggi.
I lead the delivery intelligence practice

within AWS Professional
Services Team Canada.

I have been in the practice
for five years now.

I have got promoted, I
have changed three roles

My team focuses on building
innovation solutions

Within our team, we have
people from all over the world

and they share a very different
and unique perspective.

Our leaders within Proserve
Canada are very focused
on developing growth of our people.

I love my job because
I have the opportunity
to work with the smartest people
The thing that keeps me motivated

is the learning that I
receive every single day.
